reviews.text:
This is a fantastic recipe.  I love RF Oatmeal Cookie, but I've had a hard time getting it to play nice with others.  Here it seems to combine with the toffee to create an authentic Oatmeal Cookie flavor, just as if there are bits of it mixed throughout the pudding.  Fantastic S&amp;V too, quite rare considering the type of profile.  It tastes like a pudding with the texture of frozen cool whip, with just enough crunch to make you think a soft cookie was mixed in.&#xD;
&#xD;
Fucking phenomenal stuff this is!&#xD;
&#xD;
I'm to the point now where TooTall is on my list of elite mixers who's recipes I'll make without question.  List may be a bad term, really just Id10-t and TooTall thus far!
